  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK89">
<l>uṭaimaiyu ḷiṉmai viruntōmpa lōmpā</l>
<l>maṭamai maṭavārka ṇuṇṭu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The folly that cares nothing for caring for guests—that want</l>
<l>in midst of wealth—belongs to fools.</l>
<l>(Alternative interpretation not mentioned by commentators:</l>
<l>The folly that, in midst of wealth, cares nothing for caring for guests in need</l>
<l>belongs to fools.)</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
